<i>noun</i>: 잔혹성 [잔혹썽], 잔혹 [잔혹], 악독 [악똑] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>잔혹성 [잔혹썽]</dt><br>
<dd>cruelty; harshness; brutality</dd><br>
<dd>인정이 없고 모질며 악한 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being merciless, pitiless, and malicious.</dd><br>
<dt>잔혹 [잔혹]</dt><br>
<dd>cruelty; harshness; brutality</dd><br>
<dd>인정이 없고 모질며 악함.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being merciless, pitiless, and malicious.</dd><br>
<dt>악독 [악똑]</dt><br>
<dd>viciousness; perversity; harshness</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 고약하고 독함.</dd><br>
<dd>A foul, vicious disposition.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>